This directory contains the area and world files for the main city of
Shadow-99:  The city of Stonehill.

The city is divided into seven zones, each covering a small part of the
city.  The castle, temple and university may divided into more zones if
the need arises (dungeons, catacombs, and such).

Castle    : The ??? castle, home of the royal court of the Beregunds.
Temple    : The Temple of two Gods.
University: The University.
Harbour   : The harbour area along the river.
Main      : The rest of the city; market places, city wall and such.
Stones    : The hill with the mysterious stones.
Outside   : The surrounding fields, forrest, and river.
